Package: alternc-mailman
Priority: optional
Section: admin
Architecture: all
Pre-Depends: alternc-mailman-config
Depends: alternc (>= 3.5.0~rc1), bc, mailman3-full, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Mailman module for AlternC
 AlternC is a mutualized hosting software manager for Linux.
 It allows you to manage your websites, domains, ftp, emails, aliases,
 web statistics, mailing-lists, etc.
 .
 This package is an optional module that adds mailman mailing-lists
 management to the virtual desktop. 
 .
 More information on https://www.alternc.com/

Package: alternc-mailman-config
Pre-Depends: debconf
Depends: dbconfig-mysql, python3-pymysql, python3-mysqldb, python3-authheaders, ${misc:Depends}
Priority: optional
Section: admin
Architecture: all
Description: Configuration files for alternc-mailman
 These files and dependencies are used for installing mailman3 and mailman3-web with alternc.
